No. 768,

Misc.

General Houses, Inc., v. Bruchhausen, U. S. District Judge. Horace A. Young for petitioner. Solicitor General Rankin, Assistant Attorney General Doub and Alan S. Rosenthal for Floete, Administrator of General Services, and Thomas J. McFadden for the Marloch Manufacturing Corporation et al.
